(1)
Clinton Street, south from, but not including Schermerhorn Street. On the right, is seen the U.S. Apt. House, one of Bklyn's first Apt. Houses.
June 11, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
The same, showing the foreground more clearly.
October 4, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
